":"麻彌","body":"我們Pastel＊Palettes是在東京活動的偶像團體。\n今天要走訪佐賀各地，\n把佐賀的好地方介紹給大家！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event154-03-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"我們第一站來到了，嬉野溫泉的足湯。\n一大早就有好多人來泡哦～。\n大家感覺都很舒服！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event154-03-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"現在要來採訪正在泡湯的民眾。\n請問水溫怎麼樣呢？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event154-03-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayName":"巽","body":"哎呀這溫度真是太棒了。\n不只身體會從裡面暖到外面，肌膚也變得水潤滑嫩喔。\n不愧是日本的三大美肌溫泉，真不是蓋的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-03-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDispla