內－！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-03-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"現，現在沒有跟攝影棚連線！\n我們在拍影片！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event154-03-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"攝影師A","body":"攝影暫停－。那個，不好意思……\n希望可以盡量避免主持的節奏被民眾拉走……\n我們稍微休息一下好了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"對，對不起！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event154-03-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayName":"巽","body":"好喔，你們幾個零分！　完全沒把溫泉的優點表達出來－！\n在東京可以靠那種採訪得到好棒棒印章嗎－？\n好好喔怎麼會有那麼輕鬆的工作－","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"aori02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-03-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"是啊，我們當然也想呈現出品質以上的內容。\n我們想要採訪一般居民，\n可以請你借過一下嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event154-03-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayName":"巽","body":"哼……！\n看來你們幾個有把那張殭屍臉藏好嘛","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-03-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"是的！　麻彌學姊很用心幫我們化了妝！\n簡直是大師的手藝！　是日積月累的功力！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event154-03-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"你誇，誇得太過頭了，伊芙同學。\n我只是覺得舞台用的特殊化妝應該可以派上用場，\n但其實我也以前也只有稍微學過一點點而已","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterI